page.title: 20Conclusion
page.content: We were surprised how much country- side there was around our city. Newmillerdam is visited by many people from outside the area and we hope it stays the same for many years to come. Perhaps more houses will be built and gradually the open countryside will disappear. We would like to thank all those who have helped us to find out what the area is like in l985, especially the Warden at Newmillerdam Country Park, Mr.Gordon Lunn. The people of the area who have helped the second years who have gathered information, but especially Form 2A for the interpretation of the information and preparation of this finished product.
